Total Costs = Fixed Costs + (Units Produced x (Variable Cost Per Unit))
Revenue = Units Sold x Price
Profit = Revenue - Costs

Breakeven Analysis:

Breakeven Point = Fixed Costs/(Unit Price - Unit Cost)

Cost Accounting: Cash Based & Accrual based

Cash Accounting: Good for small business, companies

Accrual Accouting: Suitable for large org, mandated by the financial regulators
